The DXJSONSchema compliance test target vendors JSON fixtures from the
JSON Schema Test Suite (https://github.com/json-schema-org/JSON-Schema-Test-Suite),
used under the MIT License, Copyright (c) 2012 Julian Berman. The fixtures are
test data only; they are not part of any shipped library product.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The DXJSONSchema library embeds the standard JSON Schema Draft 2020-12
meta-schema and its vocabulary meta-schemas, published by the JSON Schema
organization (https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema and the
.../draft/2020-12/meta/* documents). These documents are freely usable; they
are reproduced verbatim so the library can validate schema documents against
the dialect without network access.
